  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowInfoHeadless</TypeRef> constructor creates a framebuffer window binding structure and initializes the inherited <TypeRef>structureSizeInBytes</TypeRef> and type discriminator fields.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[WindowInfoHeadless(const V2UInt32& windowSizeInPixels);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="const V2UInt32&amp;" Name="windowSizeInPixels">
          The drawable framebuffer size in pixels.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
